<section>

    <div class="wrapper">
        <h1 class="main-title">Services @ Post Office</h1>

        <h2 class="sub-title">About the Karad Postal Service</h2>
        <p class="text">The Karad post office offers various services, including money orders, transactions, accounts, bill payments, and parcel delivery, ensuring reliable and accessible financial and postal solutions for all.</p>

        <div class="info-box">
            <h3 class="section-title"><i class="fas fa-money-bill-wave"></i> Money Orders</h3>
            <p class="text">India Post enables secure money transfers across the country and internationally, ensuring reliability and tracking options. The maximum amount per transaction is INR 50,000.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="info-box">
            <h3 class="section-title"><i class="fas fa-university"></i> Transactions</h3>
            <p class="text">The Post Office Savings Bank (POSB) provides multiple banking options, including savings accounts, fixed deposits, and mobile banking for ease of access.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="info-box">
            <h3 class="section-title"><i class="fas fa-file-invoice-dollar"></i> Accounts</h3>
            <ul>
                <li class="text"><b>Post Office Savings Account:</b> Secure savings with flexible withdrawals.</li>
                <li class="text"><b>National Savings Certificate (NSC):</b> Tax-saving investment.</li>
                <li class="text"><b>Public Provident Fund (PPF):</b> Long-term savings with high interest.</li>
                <li class="text"><b>Senior Citizens Savings Scheme (SCSS):</b> Designed for post-retirement financial stability.</li>
                <li class="text"><b>Sukanya Samriddhi Account (SSA):</b> For girl child savings with tax benefits.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="info-box">
            <h3 class="section-title"><i class="fas fa-receipt"></i> Bill Payment</h3>
            <p class="text">Customers can pay utility bills, including electricity, water, and gas, at the post office counters or digitally via UPI and net banking.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="info-box">
            <h3 class="section-title"><i class="fas fa-box"></i> Parcel Services</h3>
            <ul>
                <li class="text"><b>Registered Parcel:</b> Ensures safety with tracking options.</li>
                <li class="text"><b>Speed Post:</b> Fast and secure delivery service.</li>
                <li class="text"><b>Express Parcel:</b> Suitable for bulk deliveries.</li>
                <li class="text"><b>International Parcel:</b> Efficient global shipping solutions.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="highlight">
            <h3 class="sub-title">Key Features</h3>
            <ul>
                <li><i class="fas fa-hand-holding-usd"></i> Secure & efficient <b> Money Order Service.</b></li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-truck"></i> Reliable <b> Parcel Services</b> with tracking.</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-exchange-alt"></i> Easy <b>Transactions</b> with online banking support.</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-file-invoice"></i> Convenient <b>Bill Payments</b> for essential services.</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-piggy-bank"></i> Government-backed <b>Savings & Investment Schemes</b>.</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-id-card"></i> Additional services like Aadhaar updates & life insurance.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

</section>
